727
728    protected function renderItems(
729        array $items,
730        ValidationResult $filterValidationResult,
731        ?ReadableDataInterface $preparedDataReader,
732    ): string {
733        $columns = $this->getColumns();
734        $renderers = $this->getColumnRenderers();
735
736        $blocks = [];
737        $filtersForm = '';
738
739        $dataReader = $this->getDataReader();
740        $globalContext = new GlobalContext(
741            $dataReader,
742            $this->urlArguments,
743            $this->urlQueryParameters,
744            $this->translator,
745            $this->translationCategory,
746        );
747
748        if ($preparedDataReader instanceof PaginatorInterface) {
749            $pageToken = $preparedDataReader->isOnFirstPage() ? null : $preparedDataReader->getToken();
750            $pageSize = $preparedDataReader->getPageSize();
751            if ($pageSize === $this->getDefaultPageSize()) {
752                $pageSize = null;
753            }
754        } else {
755            $pageToken = null;
756            $pageSize = null;
757        }
758
759        $tags = [];
760        $hasFilters = false;
761        $filterContext = new FilterContext(
762            formId: Html::generateId(),
763            validationResult: $filterValidationResult,
764            cellInvalidClass: $this->filterCellInvalidClass,
765            errorsContainerAttributes: $this->filterErrorsContainerAttributes,
766            urlParameterProvider: $this->urlParameterProvider,
767        );
768        foreach ($columns as $i => $column) {
769            $cell = $renderers[$i] instanceof FilterableColumnRendererInterface
770                ? $renderers[$i]->renderFilter($column, new Cell(attributes: $this->filterCellAttributes), $filterContext)
771                : null;
772            if ($cell === null) {
773                $tags[] = Html::td('&nbsp;')->encode(false);
774            } else {
775                $tags[] = Html::td(attributes: $cell->getAttributes())
776                    ->content(...$cell->getContent())
777                    ->encode($cell->shouldEncode())
778                    ->doubleEncode($cell->shouldDoubleEncode());
779                $hasFilters = true;
780            }
781        }
782        if ($hasFilters) {
783            $sort = $this->urlParameterProvider?->get(
784                $this->urlConfig->getSortParameterName(),
785                $this->urlConfig->getSortParameterType()
786            );
787            $url = $this->urlCreator === null ? '' : call_user_func_array(
788                $this->urlCreator,
789                UrlParametersFactory::create(
790                    null,
791                    $this->urlConfig->getPageSizeParameterType() === UrlParameterType::PATH ? $pageSize : null,
792                    $this->urlConfig->getSortParameterType() === UrlParameterType::PATH ? $sort : null,
793                    $this->urlConfig,
794                )
795            );
796            $content = [Html::submitButton()];
797            if (!empty($pageSize) && $this->urlConfig->getPageSizeParameterType() === UrlParameterType::QUERY) {
798                $content[] = Html::hiddenInput($this->urlConfig->getPageSizeParameterName(), $pageSize);
799            }
800            if (!empty($sort) && $this->urlConfig->getSortParameterType() === UrlParameterType::QUERY) {
801                $content[] = Html::hiddenInput($this->urlConfig->getSortParameterName(), $sort);
802            }
803            $filtersForm = Html::form($url, 'GET', ['id' => $filterContext->formId, 'style' => 'display:none'])
804                ->content(...$content)
805                ->render();
806            $filterRow = Html::tr()->cells(...$tags);
807        } else {
808            $filterRow = null;
809        }
810
811        if ($this->isColumnGroupingEnabled) {
812            $tags = [];
813            foreach ($columns as $i => $column) {
814                $cell = $renderers[$i]->renderColumn($column, new Cell(), $globalContext);
815                $tags[] = Html::col($cell->getAttributes());
816            }
817            $blocks[] = Html::colgroup()->columns(...$tags)->render();
818        }
819
820        if ($this->isHeaderEnabled) {
821            $headerContext = new HeaderContext(
822                $this->getSort($dataReader),
823                $this->getSort($preparedDataReader),
824                $this->getOrderProperties(),
825                $this->sortableHeaderClass,
826                $this->sortableHeaderPrepend,
827                $this->sortableHeaderAppend,
828                $this->sortableHeaderAscClass,
829                $this->sortableHeaderAscPrepend,
830                $this->sortableHeaderAscAppend,
831                $this->sortableHeaderDescClass,
832                $this->sortableHeaderDescPrepend,
833                $this->sortableHeaderDescAppend,
834                $this->sortableLinkAttributes,
835                $this->sortableLinkAscClass,
836                $this->sortableLinkDescClass,
837                $this->keepPageOnSort ? $pageToken : null,
838                $pageSize,
839                $this->enableMultiSort,
840                $this->urlConfig,
841                $this->urlCreator,
842                $this->translator,
843                $this->translationCategory,
844            );
845            $tags = [];
846            foreach ($columns as $i => $column) {
847                $cell = $renderers[$i]->renderHeader($column, new Cell($this->headerCellAttributes), $headerContext);
848                $tags[] = $cell === null
849                    ? Html::th('&nbsp;')->encode(false)
850                    : Html::th(attributes: $cell->getAttributes())
851                        ->content(...$cell->getContent())
852                        ->encode($cell->shouldEncode())
853                        ->doubleEncode($cell->shouldDoubleEncode());
854            }
855            $headerRow = Html::tr($this->headerRowAttributes)->cells(...$tags);
856            $thead = Html::thead()->rows($headerRow);
857            if ($filterRow !== null) {
858                $thead = $thead->addRows($filterRow);
859            }
860            $blocks[] = $thead->render();
861        }
862
863        if ($this->isFooterEnabled) {
864            $tags = [];
865            foreach ($columns as $i => $column) {
866                $cell = $renderers[$i]->renderFooter(
867                    $column,
868                    (new Cell())->content('&nbsp;')->encode(false),
869                    $globalContext
870                );
871                $tags[] = Html::td(attributes: $cell->getAttributes())
872                    ->content(...$cell->getContent())
873                    ->encode($cell->shouldEncode())
874                    ->doubleEncode($cell->shouldDoubleEncode());
875            }
876            $footerRow = Html::tr($this->footerRowAttributes)->cells(...$tags);
877            $blocks[] = Html::tfoot()->rows($footerRow)->render();
878        }
879
880        $rows = [];
881        $index = 0;
882        foreach ($items as $key => $value) {
883            if ($this->beforeRowCallback !== null) {
884                /** @var Tr|null $row */
885                $row = call_user_func($this->beforeRowCallback, $value, $key, $index, $this);
886                if (!empty($row)) {
887                    $rows[] = $row;
888                }
889            }
890
891            $tags = [];
892            foreach ($columns as $i => $column) {
893                $context = new DataContext($preparedDataReader, $column, $value, $key, $index);
894                $cell = $renderers[$i]->renderBody($column, new Cell($this->bodyCellAttributes), $context);
895                $tags[] = $cell->isEmptyContent()
896                    ? Html::td($this->emptyCell, $this->emptyCellAttributes)->encode(false)
897                    : Html::td(attributes: $this->prepareBodyAttributes($cell->getAttributes(), $context))
898                        ->content(...$cell->getContent())
899                        ->encode($cell->shouldEncode())
900                        ->doubleEncode($cell->shouldDoubleEncode());
901            }
902            $bodyRowAttributes = $this->prepareBodyRowAttributes(
903                $this->bodyRowAttributes,
904                new BodyRowContext($value, $key, $index),
905            );
906            $rows[] = Html::tr($bodyRowAttributes)->cells(...$tags);
907
908            if ($this->afterRowCallback !== null) {
909                /** @var Tr|null $row */
910                $row = call_user_func($this->afterRowCallback, $value, $key, $index, $this);
911                if (!empty($row)) {
912                    $rows[] = $row;
913                }
914            }
915
916            $index++;
917        }
918        $blocks[] = empty($rows)
919            ? Html::tbody($this->tbodyAttributes)
920                ->rows(Html::tr()->cells($this->renderEmpty(count($columns))))
921                ->render()
922            : Html::tbody($this->tbodyAttributes)->rows(...$rows)->render();
923
924        return
925            $filtersForm .
926            Html::tag('table', attributes: $this->tableAttributes)->open()
927            . "\n"
928            . implode("\n", $blocks)
929            . "\n"
